6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to community health workers; creating
the Oklahoma Community Health Worker Act; providing
8 short title; defining terms; directing establishment
of certificate; making certification voluntary;
9 listing powers of community health worker; requiring
and authorizing promulgation of certain rules;
10 directing establishment of certain fees; providing
for codification; and providing an effective date.
